<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Thank You for Contacting Mahesh Gouni</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a2d4fa 0%, #124e8c 100%);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in;
    }
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3065d2 0%, #70f1f8 100%);
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #2d3436;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 30px 0;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #70f1f8 0%, #3065d2 100%);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(48, 101, 210, .3);
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(48, 101, 210, .4);
    }
    .footer {
      background: #124e8c;
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .signature {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #3065d2;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Hi, ${name}!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Thank you for contacting <strong>Mahesh Gouni</strong>! I truly appreciate you reaching out and sharing your thoughts.</p>

      <p>I will review your message and get back to you as soon as possible. If you'd like to track your request or explore more:</p>

      <a href="#" class="cta-button">Track Your Request</a>

      <p>Looking forward to assisting you!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thanks again,<br><span class="signature">Mahesh Gouni</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
